泰民宣布两年多来首次个人回归《Guilty》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/taemin-guilty-fourth-mini-album-3512130?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=taemin-guilty-fourth-mini-albumRhian Daly Tue, 10 Oct 2023 02:15:27 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3512130 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰民" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这张迷你专辑将是这位 SHINee 明星的第四张专辑</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taemin-guilty-fourth-mini-album-3512130">泰民宣布两年多来首次个人回归《Guilty》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰民" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/shinee-taemin-hard-concept-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taemin">泰民</a>公布了两年多来首次个人回归的《Guilty》的第一个细节。</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shinee">SHINee</a>歌手兼舞者最后一次发布个人作品是在 2021 年 5 月，当时他发行了迷你专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shinee-taemin-third-solo-mini-album-advice-release-date-2932421">《Advice》</a> ，该专辑是在他开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shinee-taemin-military-enlistment-may-2021-2924088">服兵役</a>前不久发行的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/taemin-kpop-shinee-superm-enlistment-advice-career-2942280">在他的第一幕中，泰民的热情和才华使他成为韩国流行音乐最可靠的王牌</a></strong></li></ul><p>《Guilty》预计于 10 月 30 日下午 6 点（韩国标准时间）（格林威治标准时间上午 9 点）上映。包括曲目列表和单曲在内的更多信息尚未透露。然而，一些与该记录相关的艺术作品已被分享。其中，一件白色衣服放在棕色地板上，旁边是一个人的鞋子和腿。迷你专辑的名称叠加在图像顶部。</p><p>服完兵役后，泰民一直忙于SHINee。该乐队于 2023 年 6 月发行了最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/shinee-hard-review-3464947">《Hard》</a> ，这也是他们成立 15 周年的纪念日。 <em>《NME》</em>在一篇三星级评论中写道：这张专辑一点也不差，但也没有达到 SHINee 所能达到的令人眼花缭乱的高度。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> TAEMIN 태민 第四张迷你专辑〖Guilty〗</p><p> ➫ 2023年10月30日下午6点（韩国时间） <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/TAEMIN?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#TAEMIN</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%ED%83%9C%EB%AF%BC?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#태민</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/SHINee?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#SHINee</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%EC%83%A4%EC%9D%B4%EB%8B%88?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#샤 Been니</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Guilty?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Guilty</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/TAEMIN_Guilty?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#TAEMIN_Guilty</a> <a href="https://t.co/vahdh71FxR">pic.twitter.com/vahdh71FxR</a></p><p> - SHINee (@SHINee) <a href="https://twitter.com/SHINee/status/1711396394781794651?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 10 月 9 日</a></p></bl